            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "If you have friends to play with, Overcooked 2 is an absolute blast.\r\n\r\nThe level design keeps things fresh throughout. Just when you think you've gotten the hang of it, the game throws a conveyor belt, a moving platform, or a completely absurd kitchen layout at you. Co-op communication becomes everything — and that's exactly where the fun (and the friendly arguments) come from."
